  9. Acceptance.

  You need not accept this License in order to receive or run a copy
of the Program. Ancillary propagation of a covered work occurring
solely as a consequence of using peer-to-peer transmission to receive
a copy likewise does not require acceptance. However, nothing other
than this License grants you permission to propagate or modify any
covered work. These actions infringe copyright if you do not accept
this License. Therefore, by modifying or conveying the Program (or
any work based on it), you indicate your acceptance of this License
and all its terms and conditions.

  10. Automatic Licensing.

  When you convey a covered work, the recipient automatically receives
a license from the original licensors, to run, modify and propagate
that work, subject to this License. You are not responsible for
complying with third-party terms of use of the work.

  11. Termination.

  Your rights under this License are automatic and will terminate if
you fail to comply. You may not knowingly propagate the Program in
violation of this License.

  12. No Surrender of Others' Freedom.

  If conditions are imposed on you (whether by court order, agreement
or otherwise) that contradict the conditions of this License, they
